file.name: ipinfodb.com-1.0-openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
servers:
  - url: https://api.ipinfodb.com
info:
  contact:
    x-twitter: ipinfodb
  description: The API returns the location of an IP address (country, region, city,
    zipcode, latitude, longitude) and the associated timezone in XML, JSON or
    plain text format.
  title: IPInfoDB IP Address Lookup
  version: "1.0"
  x-apisguru-categories:
    - location
  x-logo:
    url: https://twitter.com/ipinfodb/profile_image?size=original
  x-origin:
    - converter:
        url: https://github.com/lucybot/api-spec-converter
        version: 2.7.31
      format: openapi
      url: https://api.swaggerhub.com/apis/ipinfodb/ipinfodb-ip-address-lookup/1.0
      version: "3.0"
  x-providerName: ipinfodb.com
paths:
  /v3/ip-city/:
    get:
      description: Get location of an IP address
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: ip
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - in: query
          name: format
          schema:
            enum:
              - json
              - xml
            type: string
        - in: query
          name: key
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json; charset=utf-8:
              examples:
                "0":
                  value: '{"statusCode" : "","statusMessage" : "","ipAddress" :
                    "","countryCode" : "","countryName" : "","regionName" :
                    "","cityName" : "","zipCode" : "","latitude" :
                    "","longitude" : "","timeZone" : ""}'
              schema:
                type: string
          description: Get location information
  /v3/ip-country/:
    get:
      description: Get country of an IP address
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: ip
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - in: query
          name: key
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - in: query
          name: format
          schema:
            enum:
              - json
              - xml
            type: string
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json; charset=utf-8:
              examples:
                "0":
                  value: '{"statusCode" : "","statusMessage" : "","ipAddress" :
                    "","countryCode" : "","countryName" : ""}'
              schema:
                type: string
          description: Get country information
